{
  "stem": "1061.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Well, all that mixture, that whole conglomeration of people with us-- and not just us, but other camps being emptied-- all this mixed together.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Of course, we were-- we were-- we had clothing that was marked with a big X, both at the front and on the back.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So you could tell us a mile away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because this was white lacquer type of paint, huge.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is the way we were marked in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was the mark, the, the x.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So that if you looked at that road, you really didn't know who was who or-- and you didn't know which way the whole-- that humanity was moving.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because everything was at a standstill.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then all of a sudden, somebody comes over and says, hey, you know, there are-- there's a Swedish Red Cross here, and they have packages, Red Cross packages for us.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "First time in, in, in a-- years I've got a can of sardines.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And how the Swedish Red Cross happened to be there at that time, I really don't know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, we only know one thing, and that is that President Roosevelt died.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because my sister overhead it on the radio, while she was cleaning the office.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And that was April 14.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we didn't know anything other than that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, when we found ourselves on that road that was so clogged with everybody, and, and, and nobody knew who was who and what was happening, and planes were flying over, and-- among the girls, the women, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that we worked with, you know, the girls who were serving the Germans, who also carried those bags for the Germans, as I did, the personal maids, was one woman, Halina.",
      "word_count": 72
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she, she had an idea.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If we separated ourselves from these German women whom we served-- if she-- she spoke German very well-- if she got dressed in one of the uniforms out of the rucksack that she carried or I carried or whoever carried, the maids-- if we separated ourselves, she could impersonate a German woman and say that we just got lost, 12 of us, we just got-- you know.",
      "word_count": 67
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because we couldn't hide who we were, because we were painted with those, with those crosses, which is the exactly what we did.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We-- people, you know, people were getting their rations.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, and everything was stuck in the way.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the German women, of course, helped themselves to the cigarettes that were being given out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And you know, they were such-- well, that's another story.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were really worse than men, in-- in many respects.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They-- you could never imagine that a woman could be as cruel and brutal as these women were.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Anyhow, we detached ourselves, 12 of us, altogether.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And Halina was our so-called overseer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we-- because the road was in the middle, and there were two embankments, we slid down the embankment and there were hay in the, in the field.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We hid behind the hay.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we stayed there, I think, overnight.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And Halina got herself dressed as an SS woman.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then meanwhile, whatever happened, the, the traffic got to move a little.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And probably-- nobody would ever miss us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We knew that for sure.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Nobody would miss us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we met a Polish Christian who was employed at the farm nearby.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he said that they all ran away, that there is a villa there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we should go and tell the woman-- there's an old woman there, or young woman, whatever-- there's a woman attendant, an attendant, to feed us.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Well, we actually did what he said.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We went to the house.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "There was the German woman.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It was a villa.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We thought it was fantastic.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And we were going to see what happens now.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We found out that there is a Russian offensive around.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And that they-- on the west, from the west, there is another offensive coming.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "While we were in that villa, the Russians came.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Meaning they arrived at the villa, and they wanted to know who was living here, and who were these people were.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And we told them who we are.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Halina, I think, spoke Russian also.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] They said, oh great.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "You are here, that's good.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "We come tomorrow, you're going to be working for us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Meanwhile, there was a Russian woman among us, who also said-- she warned us that they rape women, and we better get out of here, which we did.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "The following day, we started a trek back to Poland.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Because we really had no idea, now, what happened to the family, to the extended family that I told you about, Babcia Tenenblum.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We knew because the Russians were there.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
